Copy the files as follows to install JOGL and JOAL on your system:

Linux	(adjust the path of your JRE)
	cp *.jar /opt/sunjdk-1.4.2.10/jre/lib/ext
	cp linux-i586/*.so* /opt/java-1.4.2.10/jre/lib/i386

Windows	(adjust the path of your JRE)
	copy *.jar "C:\Program Files\Java 1.4\jre\lib\ext
	copy win32/*.dll "C:\Program Files\Java 1.4\jre\bin
	execute OpenALwEAX.exe

OS X	(should work out of the box)
	cp *.jar /System/Library/Java/Extensions
	cp macosx-universal/*.jnilib /System/Library/Java/Extensions
